OL,3,CCharity secures town apartments for
OL,4,Cadults with learning disabilities
OL,6,FJersey charity Les Amis has secured 13
OL,7,Fresidential homes after exchanging the
OL,8,Fformer Hampshire Hotel to Andium Homes.
OL,10,FThe homes are located at the Lime
OL,11,Fdevelopment in Green Street, St
OL,12,FHelier, which they will turn into
OL,13,Fspecialist homes for islanders with
OL,14,Flearning disabilities.
OL,16,FAndium Homes has acquired Hampshire
OL,17,FHotel to enhance its North of St
OL,18,FHelier regeneration programme.
