OL,3,CCharity secures town apartments for
OL,4,Cadults with learning disabilities
OL,6,FLes Amis had originally planned to
OL,7,Fturn the former Hampshire Hotel into
OL,8,Fspecialist homes for people with
OL,9,Fdisabilities.
OL,11,FPlanning permission was granted in
OL,12,FNovember 2022 to convert the site.
OL,14,FHowever, the organisation pulled the
OL,15,Fplug on the project after the Jersey
OL,16,Fgovernment withdrew its support in
OL,17,FMarch 2023.
OL,19,FAt the time, officials said the
OL,20,Fdevelopment would be "too large" for
OL,21,Fthe island's needs.
