OL,3,CCharity secures town apartments for
OL,4,Cadults with learning disabilities
OL,6,FLes Amis' Managing Director, Shaun
OL,7,FFindlay, said: "After last year's
OL,8,Fsetback with Project Maison des Amis,
OL,9,Fwe were looking for a solution that
OL,10,Fmet our service users' needs without
OL,11,Fthe added risks of developing bespoke
OL,12,Ffacilities in the current economic
OL,13,Fclimate.
OL,15,F"They say as one door closes, another
OL,16,Fopens; in this case, 13 doors opened."
